text: People Will Talk is a 1935 American romantic comedy movie directed by Alfred Santell and starring Charlie Ruggles, Mary Boland, Leila Hyams, Dean Jagger, Cecil Cunningham, Edward Brophy. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1935 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Alfred Santell
